snippet.title: tennis-esports | Virtual Reality Tennis Simulator | for Oculus Quest 2
snippet.description:
Tennis Esports is a virtual tennis game for Oculus Quest 2 on the meta Oculus Store that offers you a whole range of exciting features.

Multiplayer VR Tennis in the Metaverse is played with a virtual racket, with virtual balls on a virtual court - virtually anywhere. All you need to play VR Tennis today is a VR Headset Oculus Quest 2 and Download the App (Link below). Exhibiting at the US-Open 2022 together with Wilson you can experience how they come as close as possible to the real tennis sports.

In the training mode you can practice different levels of difficulty at home or for your competition. Challenge yourself with Mirrorplay, a new and fascinating way of playing VR Tennis. Achieve personal bests in high score competitions.

Choose a match and play against others online! Enter a stadium and feel like a professional while you play.

Download here: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4872542182873415/
Join the chat: https://discord.com/invite/8rcSArKJD4
More information: https://tennis-esports.com
